			<p align="center"><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a class="logo-anchor" href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fwww.taskade.com/1/0100019379cbdb87-2047cca3-8e8e-4216-9db6-165ca92b95b3-000000/0y5X6u18WcKOQP19XiS4zZ1c-bg=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: underline; color: #ff2d60; display: block;"><img class="left" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1666116818.png" style="border: 0px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; width: 42px; height: 42px;" /></a></span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;">Hi there  🐑</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;">Transform your projects with Project Views — your productivity Origami! 🦩 Like shaping paper into art, fold your project into multiple forms without altering its core.</span></p>

			<p> </p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">✍️ List / Outline View</h1>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;">Perfect for tasks, agendas, and note-taking. Ideal when you want to work from top to bottom, capturing ideas quickly. 👉 Use Case: Great for meeting agendas, daily to-do lists, and brainstorming sessions. <a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F12757582963091/1/0100019379cbdb87-2047cca3-8e8e-4216-9db6-165ca92b95b3-000000/8YqEjEWawddzkbg0sKMew7lBIE0=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>.</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698689136.png" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title"> </h1>

			<p> </p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">📋 Board / Kanban View</h1>

			<p>Visualize tasks in columns, making it easy to manage project phases or categories. 👉 Use Case: Ideal for development sprints, content calendars, and workflow management. <span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F10460110476179/1/0100019379cbdb87-2047cca3-8e8e-4216-9db6-165ca92b95b3-000000/TtxkYMYvlpLMtNYN6B-s91q8buo=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a></span>.</p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI Research" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698689170.gif" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title"> </h1>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title"> </h1>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">🗓 Calendar View</h1>

			<p>See tasks and deadlines in a calendar layout, and visualize upcoming tasks due for any project. 👉 Use Case: Perfect for managing deadlines, scheduling meetings, and tracking milestones. <span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F5260144580499/1/0100019379cbdb87-2047cca3-8e8e-4216-9db6-165ca92b95b3-000000/3_J54S08unT-Xn2vxafcfcdO11Q=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>.</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI Research" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698689145.png" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

			<p> </p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">📊 Action View</h1>

			<p>Display tasks in a table with customizable columns. 👉 Use Case: Best for tracking project status, assigning tasks, and customer relationship management.  <span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F10488503329683/1/0100019379cbdb87-2047cca3-8e8e-4216-9db6-165ca92b95b3-000000/zP5YIMe2WrVf17kElbWI5Da2lX4=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>.</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI Research" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698689252.png" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title"> </h1>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">🧠 Mind Map View</h1>

			<p>Visualize complex ideas, projects, and workflows. 👉 Use Case: Excellent for brainstorming sessions, flowcharts, and project planning. <span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F12757664773139/1/0100019379cbdb87-2047cca3-8e8e-4216-9db6-165ca92b95b3-000000/iPzAArD_QYLSvoCvScUl_ThDTzo=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>.</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI Research" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698689185.png" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

			<p> </p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">▲ Organizational Chart View</h1>

			<p>Visualize your project or team in a hierarchical structure to see the bigger picture. 👉 Use Case: Team onboarding, departmental planning, workflow optimization, and stakeholder mapping.  <span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F12757682226963/1/0100019379cbdb87-2047cca3-8e8e-4216-9db6-165ca92b95b3-000000/YUp0suBimPvRnuir4kmFHYZjMbc=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>.</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI Research" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698689224.gif" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

